::KitKat::

She looked at Megatron. "Well now, if everything is to yur 
satisfaction, I will get things ready." She turned to 
Destructor. "Have War or Famine monitor the bridge. I want to know 
the ssecond the Allience base sets down and where. Then we will march 
on them." She leaned closer to Destructor to whisper to him. "If you 
wold be so kind as to do so, I'd appreciate it."

She turned back to Aracnia and Megatron. "Is there anything else that 
we need to discuss? Untill the Allience base comes to rest, we can do 
little more than what we have already done."
